metadata.description: At InnerCircleAlpha, we believe in cutting through the noise and clutter of typical pump and dump degen plays. We aim to provide clear and concise information about projects in a non-hype-based way. We offer weekly live streams that are recorded and archived for future viewing, as well as numerous other voice chat sessions within the server. Our content is to be viewed as educational information, not investment advice. With a limited number of members, we are able to focus on building quality performers within our own community and maintain an optimal information flow to or community. Access to InnerCircleAlpha also provides dual membership to https://impressumtrading.com/, where your educational experience can continue at no additional cost to you.
metadata.name: InnerCircle AlphaPass #1
